Program: Great Lives
Title: Sir Thomas Beecham
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00js9g1
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 26 May 2017
Matthew Parris presents the biographical series in which his guests choose someone who has inspired their lives. Politician and broadcaster David Mellor promotes the life of Sir Thomas Beecham, conductor and founder of the Royal Philharmonic Orchestra. He was known for his wit and energy, which spawned a huge number of anecdotes, but which of them are true? Show less